Algoritmo CalculateAvarage
	//Request the 5 ratings from the user
	Escribir "Enter First grade"
	Leer rating1
	Escribir "Enter the second grade"
	Leer rating2
	Escribir "Enter the third grade"
	Leer rating3
	Escribir "Enter the fourth grade"
	Leer rating4
	Escribir "Emter the five grade"
	Leer rating5
	//Calculate the avarage
	avarage = (rating1 + rating2 + rating3 + rating4 + rating5)/5
	//Show the result
	Escribir "The avarage of the 5 ratings is:" ,avarage
FinAlgoritmo
